keyFacts: The document is a passenger manifest for Jeffrey Epstein's private jet (tail number N908JE, a Boeing 727) operated by JEGE, INC.
The flight occurred on November 1, 2004, with a destination of New York.
Jeffrey Epstein and Ghislaine Maxwell are explicitly listed as passengers #1 and #2.
The manifest contains numerous other passenger entries (up to 26) that appear to be partially redacted, illegible, or contain placeholder text.
The flight originated from an unspecified location, indicated only by a placeholder or redaction in the 'FROM' field.
